{"tid":890210,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"日本人做乜撚嘢？","createTime":"2018-11-05T06:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T04:26:12.000Z","uid":20835,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"892835d2cd98cf19d6089160ac12ef2a890ec621","tid":890210,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:52:25.000Z","msg":"繼Hello Kitty「不是貓」之後，日本吉祥物界又有震撼彈！熊本縣紅遍海內外的吉祥物、港台粉絲都十分喜愛的熊本熊原來不是熊，而且也不叫「熊本熊」，官方中文名其實是叫「酷MA萌」。<br />\n<br />\n日本《朝日新聞》記者為了調查「酷MA萌」名字的普及程度，6月時在熊本市中央區「酷MA萌廣場」訪問來自中港台以及馬來西亞等地50名遊客，提供「熊本熊」以及「酷MA萌」兩個選項，問他們是如何稱呼這隻非常鬼馬的黑色吉祥物，結果50人當中有43人選了「熊本熊」。來自台灣的33歲遊客許晉誠表示︰「沒聽過酷MA萌，在台灣大家都稱之為熊本熊。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前寵物小精靈都俾你兜話講普通話嘅人多啲所以叫做寶可夢 你話依家呢個做乜撚嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f3aa4077a0eba3ead908c7925f0610acf3dcfb","tid":890210,"uid":20835,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20150413/photo/0413-00423-002b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20150413%2Fphoto%2F0413-00423-002b1.jpg&h=97446e02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熊本熊：屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0846fbc743624dc356d61341d66cae82f01e6263","tid":890210,"uid":34243,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:54:51.000Z","msg":"酷MA萌一樣係普通話譯音黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce27c11ef04f42351c131e8c5d6c33225ba9760c","tid":890210,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:55:47.000Z","msg":"原文呢？"},{"pid":"67032c3935a4dbb6afc4203afeca695b7ac1f89b","tid":890210,"uid":72304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:55:49.000Z","msg":"官方中文名但有英文係入面?<img src=\"/ass